td><pre><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">mapper</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token name\">PUBLIC</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN\"</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token string\">\"http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mapper</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">namespace</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>com.example.mapper.UserMapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>select</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>findAll<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">resultType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>com.example.entity.User<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>        SELECT * FROM user</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>    </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>select</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>findById<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">parameterType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>java.lang.Integer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">resultType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>com.example.entity.User<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre>        SELECT * FROM user WHERE id = #&#123;id&#125;</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mapper</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"常見問題與解決方案\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#常見問題與解決方案\">#</a> 常見問題與解決方案</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-配置問題\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-配置問題\">#</a> 1. 配置問題</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>確保所有配置文件的位置正確</li>\n<li>檢查依賴版本的兼容性</li>\n<li>注意 XML 文件的命名空間</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-數據庫連接問題\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-數據庫連接問題\">#</a> 2. 數據庫連接問題</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>檢查數據庫連接信息</li>\n<li>確保數據庫驅動正確</li>\n<li>測試數據庫連接是否可用</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-mapper映射問題\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-mapper映射問題\">#</a> 3. Mapper 映射問題</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>確保 Mapper 接口和 XML 文件對應</li>\n<li>檢查 SQL 語句的正確性</li>\n<li>注意參數類型的匹配</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"項目實戰經驗\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#項目實戰經驗\">#</a> 項目實戰經驗</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-代碼組織\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-代碼組織\">#</a> 1. 代碼組織</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>遵循三層架構：控制層、服務層、數據訪問層</li>\n<li>合理規劃包結構</li>\n<li>統一命名規範</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-性能優化\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-性能優化\">#</a> 2. 性能優化</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>使用緩存機制</li>\n<li>優化 SQL 語句</li>\n<li>合理使用連接池</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-安全考慮\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-安全考慮\">#</a> 3. 安全考慮</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>參數校驗</li>\n<li>SQL 注入防護</li>\n<li>權限控制</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"總結\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#總結\">#</a> 總結</h2>\n<p>SSM 框架的學習需要循序漸進，從基礎配置開始，逐步深入到各個框架的特性和使用技巧。MyBatis 作為持久層框架，其直觀的 SQL 管理方式確實更適合初學者。在實際開發中，需要注意以下幾點：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>理解框架的核心概念</li>\n<li>熟練掌握配置方法</li>\n<li>多練習，多實踐</li>\n<li>注意代碼規範</li>\n<li>持續學習新特性</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"參考資源\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#參考資源\">#</a> 參考資源</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Spring 官方文檔</li>\n<li>MyBatis 官方文檔</li>\n<li>黑馬程序員教程</li>\n<li>GitHub 優秀開源項目</li>\n<li>技術社區分享</li>\n</ol>\n<p>希望這份學習筆記能夠幫助到同樣在學習 SSM 框架的朋友們。如有問題，歡迎交流討論。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"# 自從看了 \"用 springboot 建立一個小而美的 blog\"B 站視頻後，就發現如今若是要建立一個博客，可能相對於 jpa 來說 mybatics 更...","permalink":"/post/68222b82643fcc43d84fa4d6c522dc13","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.5k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"coding","slug":"coding","count":3,"path":"api/categories/coding.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"科技","slug":"科技","count":5,"path":"api/tags/科技.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%BE%9E%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%86%E7%94%A8springboot%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%B0%8F%E8%80%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84blogb%E7%AB%99%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%B1%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%A6%82%E4%BB%